setMergeSource

public void setMergeSource(ItemIdentifier mergeSource)
Sets the Item that acted as the source in the merge operation that created the version described by this VersionInfo to the one with the specified ItemIdentifier. When getMergeSource() returns a non-null value, getVersionChangeType() must return VersionChangeType.DATA.

Parameters:
mergeSource - The ItemIdentifier of the Item that acted as the source in the merge operation.

4.0
